name: Scooter Girl Pillowcase - Olive Green
description:
Scooter Girl is one of those great designs on our pillowcases that makes everyone smile. Who doesn't want to be on a vintage scooter heading out of town for a jaunt!

My husband had a 1959 All State Scooter that we loved. That was the inspiration for this image. It is featured in either an olive green, but also comes in a soft blue gray. These are hand screened onto white cotton blend pillowcases. They are standard size cases and come two per package.

Each set comes in a plastic sleeve package with a Maynard's Mousetrap header card.

name: 2 Headed Snake T-shirt
description:
We are featuring the 2 Headed Cobra image on 100% grey soft cotton. The artist is my husband, Johnny Mojo and he creates great images that can be worn by all types of folks. American Sideshow is his logo. The graphic is flawless and original.

Bucking the trend in T-shirts too, he pledges that no clip-art or focus groups were used in the making of these shirt graphics. Only high quality slim-fit T-shirts printed with waterbased inks for a crisp look and soft feel; perfect for showcasing Mojo’s artwork.

I have MEDIUM Only

name: Mermaid T-shirt
description:
We are featuring the popular mermaid image on 100% soft cotton. The artist is my husband, Johnny Mojo and he creates great images that can be worn by all types of folks. American Sideshow is his logo. The graphic is flawless and original. We silkscreen the mermaid image in a soft gray on black shirt.

Bucking the trend in T-shirts too, he pledges that no clip-art or focus groups were used in the making of these shirt graphics. Only high quality slim-fit T-shirts printed with waterbased inks for a crisp look and soft feel; perfect for showcasing Mojo’s artwork.

I have XL, Large, and Small.

name: Swing Dancer Tote Bag
description: This cute canvas tote bag has our Maynard's Mousetrap Swing Dancer image silkscreened in Royal Blue ink. The tote bag measures 14 1/2" x 14" with 20" canvas straps. The tote bag is perfect for the market or library or dance class! It is perfect as a gift for friends, acquaintances, or you! The blue ink in the close up photo is textured and comes out a little fuzzy looking in the photo. In real life it is very clear and defined.

name: Robot Pillowcase - Blue
description:
BLUE Robot 100% Cotton Pillowcases are here! We have found this to be one of our most popular designs. The orange robot is on the moon's surface with planets and rockets in its atmosphere. It is great for children and adults and everyone and anyone.

They come in a set of 2 packaged in a plastic sleeve with a Maynard's Mousetrap header card. The cases are 100% cotton white cases and hand screened with blue water based ink that does not fade! I have been making these for over 12 years and they do not fade. This is a copyrited image by Maynard's Mousetrap.

name: Western Pillowcase - Red
description:
Giddy Up to bed Little Doggies...

Here are our Western Cowboy Pillowcases shown in a sage green hand screen image on white standard size pillowcases. These were designed to pay homage to old Westerns of the 1940's and 1950's. We have a collage of essential cowboy ware and accessories spread about the design. Horseshoe, guitar, branding irons, cow skull, and spur surround our happy horseman.

These have been popular with those who cherish the old nickle matinees, the horse enthusiast, and the little cowfolk. But they are for all to enjoy and come ready to you in a plastic sleeve package with a Maynard's Mousetrap header card. Each set includes 2 cases and are ready to give to all your friends, family, teachers, and yourself!

name: Good Luck Pillowcases - Mint Green
description:
Good Luck Symbols come in many ways. We included several in our Good Luck Pillowcase designs. And can't we all use a little good luck? Sleep on these cases every night and just soak in all that luck!

On this design, we have lucky die, a wishbone, the lucky 7 and 13, a shamrock, and the opened horse shoe. These are hand screened in a mint green ink. The pillowcases are standard size and white cotton blend.

Each set will come to you with 2 pillowcases in a plastic sleeve package with a Maynard's Mousetrap header card. They are great for everyone in your life, especially those a little down on their luck.

name: Hula Girl Pillowcase - Mint Green
description:
Hulas and Tikis all in one setting! Ah, the Islands! We wanted to honor one of our favorite places - Hawaii, in our Maynard's Mousetrap pillowcase set.

We have mint green hula girl pillowcases for you to chose from. The Hula girl image is hand screened with water based ink. The MINT GREEN cases are 100% white cotton pillowcases with a 220 thread count. Look for our TAN Hula cases in our listings. Both are soft and lovely!

Each set includes 2 standard sized cases packaged in a plastic sleeve with a Maynard's header card. They are completely ready for you to give to friends, family, teachers, Ukelele teachers, Hula dancers, hostesses, or any great person in your life! Spread the joy and thank you for looking our way!

name: Kool Kars Pillowcases - Sage Green
description:
Here is another creation we came up with for Maynard's Mousetrap pillowcases and linens. Kool Kars is a collage of vintage images from those classic cars of the 1950's and 1960's. In the collage, you will see a steering wheel, dashboard, V8 logo, and other iconic images from those beautiful automobiles. On top of those images are several cool vehicles. We have always been inspired by the classic cars and enjoy our 1954 Chevy Wagon!

This set includes two white standard pillowcases. They are a cotton blend with a T-180 thread count. Wash them as often as you please, the image is available in a medium sage green. This same design also comes in a blue gray ink. The ink does not fade. These are hand screened with water based inks.

These come packaged in a plastic sleeve with a Maynard's Mousetrap header card. They are ready to give to friends, family, teachers, hostesses, and those fabulous folk who brighten up your days!

name: Sunny Pillowcases
description:
Happy Flowers!

Here are our Sunny Flower Pillowcases shown in a yellow hand screen image on white 100% cotton standard size pillowcases. These were designed to pay homage to old sunkist style ads for juice of the 1940's and 1950's. Flowers are spread about the design bordered by a daisy chain.

These happen to be my favorite of all of our copyrighted designs. It just makes me happy. But they are for all to enjoy and come ready to you in a plastic sleeve package with a Maynard's Mousetrap header card. Each set includes 2 cases and are ready to give to all your friends, family, teachers, and yourself!

name: Charm Bracelet Pillowcase
description:
You could always hear my Mom coming because her charms would bang together and make a wonderful racket. I have a charm bracelet today and so do my nieces and other fun gals in my life. We put the charm bracelet design together to celebrate all those cool gals who love their dangling jewelry.

Our charm bracelet is shown in a blue gray ink or a mint green ink. The image is hand screened onto cotton blend standard sized white pillowcases. There are 14 charms on this bracelet and that includes a guitar, a baby carriage, a heart locket, a sombrero, and a 4 leaf clover. There are many fun charms shown.

Our cases come as a set of 2 packaged in a plastic sleeve with a Maynard's Mousetrap header card. They will be ready to give to a favorite gal, your grandmother, your best friend, or yourself!

name: Guardian Angel Pillowcase
description:
The Guardian Angel pillowcase set includes 2 standard cases with a T-180 thread count. They are a cotton blend white case with a one color hand screened design. We have the Guardian Angel cases in Blue Gray, Sage, or a Soft Gray. They come completely packaged in a plastic sleeve with a header card.

"Guardian Angel....Watch Over Me" is featured on the cases and adorned with praying hands and of course, the Guardian Angel.

name: Cherry Pillowcases
description:
We love the kitschy look of cherries. It just makes your day brighter to see a splash of cherries in your home! We created these pillowcases to make the bedroom a better place to be. These were especially inspired by all those young gals out there who are not afraid of color!

In each package, there will be 2 cotton blend standard size pillowcases. The cherries design is hand screened with red water based ink. The ink has not faded on our cases in over 11 years of producing these fun images.

These will arrive to you packaged in a plastic sleeve with a Maynard's Mousetrap header card. They are ready to give to neighbors doing you good deeds, family, friends, and yourself!

name: Lucky in Love Pillowcases
description:
After visiting Memphis and seeing A. Schwabs's Pharmacy, we had to create a pillowcase design that honored all those great love potions and powders!

This is a cupid's delight pillowcase design. Lucky in Love is one of our fastest moving designs.  I also have them in pink.

Perfect for the love in your life or to give to the newly wed couple or the couple who have been betrothed for 50 years! What a kick that would be!

They come 2 cases in a set and are packaged in a plastic sleeve with a Maynard's Mousetrap Header card. They are ready to give or get.  

Sweet Dreams!
